          "type": "markdown",
          "title": "Approach",
          "content": "### Why Elasticsearch?\n\nWe evaluated Typesense, Meilisearch, and Elasticsearch. Elasticsearch won on:\n\n- **Scale**: Handles our 148k product catalog with room to grow\n- **Faceting**: Native support for multi-level category filtering\n- **Team familiarity**: Two engineers have prior Elasticsearch experience\n\n### Index Strategy\n\nWe're using a single `products` index with these analyzed fields:\n- `name` (boosted 3x)\n- `description` (standard analyzer)\n- `tags` (keyword)\n- `category_path` (path hierarchy tokenizer)"
